3. Steps to clear out the history of a git/github repository
https://gist.github.com/stephenhardy/5470814
-- Remove the history from
rm -rf .git

#remove git stage area
git reset

-- recreate the repos from the current content only
git init

git reset --mixed master
git add .
git commit -m "This is a new commit for laraveldemo"
git remote add origin https://github.com/aidenjspang/laraveldemo.git
git push origin master



Removing files from a repository's history
https://help.github.com/articles/removing-files-from-a-repository-s-history/

