## Sample
1. 1st Commit
git reset
git init
git add .
git commit -m "1st commit"
git remote add origin https://github.com/aidenjspang/laraveldemo.git
git push -u origin master

2. Update
git add .  (삭제된 폴더 반영을 위해서는 git add --all)
git commit -m "2nd commit"
git push -u origin master


3. Git repository 의 History를 Delete 하려면
rm -rf .git
git init
git remote add origin https://github.com/aidenjspang/laraveldemo.git
git add .
git commit -m "1st commit"
git push -f origin master

